	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />To turn a colormap into a palette, do Windows &gt; Dockable Dialogs &gt; Palettes, right-click inside the box, and choose Import Palette...<br /><br />To apply a colormap to an image, do Colors &gt; Map &gt; Set Colormap...

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


